    slug: "clinging-to-the-quran-and-sunnah",
    title: "Clinging to the Qur'an and Sunnah",
    summary: "This article explains the clear and preserved sources a Muslim always returns back to; the Qur'an and Sunnah, upon the understanding of the Salaf.",
